Module kivakit.core
Package com.telenav.kivakit.core.language.reflection.property

Class PropertyFilterSet

java.lang.Object
com.telenav.kivakit.core.language.reflection.property.PropertyFilterSet
All Implemented Interfaces:
PropertyFilter
Direct Known Subclasses:
AllFields, ConversionPropertyFilterSet
public class PropertyFilterSet extends Object implements PropertyFilter
Base class for property filters. Supports Java Beans and KivaKit style accessor naming conventions with the enum PropertyNamingConvention and filtering of properties and fields with PropertyMembers. The constructor takes a style and a set of explicit includes (nothing is included by default). Static fields and properties are never included. Any field or method tagged with KivaKitExcludeProperty will be excluded regardless of the inclusions specified.

Subclasses can utilize the following tests to implement filters that don't follow the pattern implemented by this base class.

Getters and Setters

  • isGetter(Method) - True if the method is a getter under the given naming convention
  • isSetter(Method) - True if the method is a setter under the given naming convention

Include Tests

  • isIncluded(Method) - True if the method is included under the given set of PropertyMemberss
  • isIncluded(Field) - True if the field is included under the given set of PropertyMemberss

KivaKit Annotation Tests

  • isKivaKitIncluded(Method) - True if the method is annotated with KivaKitIncludeProperty
  • isKivaKitIncluded(Field) - True if the field is annotated with KivaKitIncludeProperty
  • isKivaKitExcluded(Method) - True if the method is annotated with KivaKitExcludeProperty
  • isKivaKitExcluded(Field) - True if the field is annotated with KivaKitExcludeProperty
